{"tid":511951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真正金主？ 康宏涉向黃浩借出近1億元收購一間本地傳媒","createTime":"2017-12-28T03:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T04:07:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8bf0093846d7c57658f91cb5fbca041f54ee25e3","tid":511951,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171227/57633734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57633734&d=3Q0axaAZ8itZuAOIHRvp%2Ff7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=46cdef09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57633734&h=ac7883ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171227/57633734</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171227/large/1514385181_628a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171227%2Flarge%2F1514385181_628a.jpg&h=a1e43681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n康宏（1019）爆出高層涉貪案後，事件逐步發酵。有消息向本報指，康宏曾向商人黃浩借出近1億元貸款。本報向黃浩查詢，惟他未有正面回應借錢一事。<br />\n<br />\n黃浩今年7月出售《都市日報》予本港金融公司，代價4億元；同月隨即公佈，收購壹傳媒（282）旗下《壹週刊》港台業務。然而，《壹週刊》交易遲遲未能完成，數度延遲最終限期，壹傳媒早前更表明或尋求法律意見。目前最後交易日期延至明年2月28日，而1月2日（下周二）須就本港資產繳付1.08億元、台灣資產的初步保證金4000萬元，黃浩就交易進展表示「looking forward」。<br />\n<br />\n據《香港01》報道，康宏新任首席財務總監近日調查後，發現更多問題貸款、或資金被不當轉移或使用，當中包括一筆近億元資金，懷疑遭不當轉移，用以收購一間本地傳媒。"},{"pid":"f3e70a3fcb818dd23612b832a79ffd0e704563a3","tid":511951,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎米路被斷。"}]}